%% Supplier Portal — Phase 1: Core Onboarding & Compliance
%% Split from 01_e2e_process_flow.mmd

flowchart TB
    A([Supplier Manager<br/>logs into Apollo Platform]) --> B[Navigate to<br/>Supplier Portal Module]
    B --> C{Invitation<br/>Method?}

    C -->|Individual| D[Open Supplier Onboarding<br/>Invitation E-Form Modal]
    C -->|Bulk CSV| E[Upload CSV File<br/>with Supplier List]

    D --> F[Fill: Name, Email,<br/>ERP/Company, Category]
    E --> G[Validate CSV:<br/>Duplicates, Format, Email]

    F --> H[Send Invitation Email<br/>with Secure Time-Limited Link]
    G --> H

    H --> I([Supplier Receives Email<br/>from noreply@qas.com])
    I --> J[Click: Proceed To Complete<br/>Vendor Registration]

    J --> K[Step 1: General Supplier Info<br/>Name, Email, TIN, Tax Classification]
    K --> L[Step 2: Purchase Info<br/>Sales Rep, Billing & Shipping Address]
    L --> M[Step 3: Remittance Info<br/>Multiple Addresses via Grid CRUD]
    M --> N[Step 4: Payment Info<br/>Wire/ACH, Bank Name, Account, ABA]
    N --> O[Step 5: Upload Documents<br/>Multi-file, Drag-Drop, Type Selection]

    O --> P[Certify & Submit Registration]
    P --> Q{Auto-Save<br/>Draft?}
    Q -->|Yes — Resume Later| K
    Q -->|Submit| R

    R[AGENT: Supplier Screening<br/>Automated — Parallel Checks] --> S1[Address Verification]
    R --> S2[TIN Validation]
    R --> S3[Sanctions Screening<br/>OFAC/EU/UN]
    R --> S4[AGENT: Bank Account<br/>Validation — Automated]

    S1 --> T{All Checks<br/>Passed?}
    S2 --> T
    S3 --> T
    S4 --> T

    T -->|Any Failed| U[Block with Actionable<br/>Error + Retry Option]
    U --> R

    T -->|All Passed| V[AGENT: Supplier Approval<br/>Assisted — Multi-Level Workflow]

    V --> W{Approval<br/>Decision?}
    W -->|Approved| X[Activate Supplier<br/>+ Grant Portal Access via Keycloak]
    W -->|Rejected| Y[Notify Supplier<br/>of Rejection with Reason]
    W -->|Reassigned| V
    W -->|SLA Breach| Z[Auto-Escalate to<br/>Next Approval Level]
    Z --> V

    X --> AA([Supplier Dashboard<br/>Financial Summary + Tasks + Alerts])

    style R fill:#ff6b6b,color:#fff
    style S4 fill:#ff6b6b,color:#fff
    style V fill:#ffa726,color:#fff
